window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When sudden emergencies arise, James Bond is there to meet them. Whether dealing with the assassination of a Cuban thug in America, the destruction of an international heroin ring, or a mysterious death in the Seychelles, 007 gets the job done in his own unmistakable style. </p> <p>Contains the short stories \"From a View to a Kill\", \"For Your Eyes Only\", \"Quantum of Solace\", \"Risico\", and \"The Hildebrand Rarity.\" </p> <p>This audiobook includes an exclusive bonus interview with Samuel West. </p> <p>Blackstone Audio, Inc. James Bond and 007 are registered trademarks of Danjaq LLC, used under license by Ian Fleming Publications Ltd</p>"; 
